CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Presurance Holdings, Inc. is a Michigan-based insurance holding company. Through its insurance carrier subsidiaries, Presurance provides specialty property/casualty insurance on both an admitted and non-admitted basis throughout the United States. Presurance is an innovative company targeting niche markets with tailored products to meet the specialized needs of insureds.
